---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Vibe AI Infrastructure"
  description="Learn AGI infrastructure through Vibe learning with Vibe Nano and Vibe Insights."
>
  <main class="landing reveal">
    <section class="hero">
      <p class="eyebrow">Learn AGI Infrastructure via Vibe Learning</p>
      <h1>Vibe AI Infrastructure</h1>
      <p class="hero-copy">
        Vibe AI Infra is a learning-first infrastructure program for the AGI era. We combine
        hands-on system building in <strong>Vibe Nano</strong> with transparent analysis in
        <strong> Vibe Insights</strong>, so every concept links to concrete engineering work.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="vision-strip">
      <p>
        Vision: make AGI infrastructure understandable, reproducible, and composable across
        silicon, software, and operations.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="focus-grid">
      <a href="/nano-infra" class="focus-card nano">
        <span class="badge">Build</span>
        <h2>Vibe Nano</h2>
        <p>
          Navigate the project map, open each project page, and learn why each layer matters for AGI
          infrastructure.
        </p>
        <span class="jump">Explore Projects</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/insights" class="focus-card insights">
        <span class="badge">Analyze</span>
        <h2>Vibe Insights</h2>
        <p>
          Study performance and cost models with practical assumptions and implementation-oriented
          next steps.
        </p>
        <span class="jump">Read Insights</span>
      </a>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .landing {
    max-width: 1120px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 88px 20px 98px;
  }

  .hero {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  .eyebrow::before {
    content: '>';
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    line-height: 0.98;
    font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 8vw, 6rem);
    max-width: 14ch;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .eyebrow::before {
    content: '>';
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    line-height: 0.98;
    font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 8vw, 6rem);
    max-width: 14ch;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    text-shadow: 0 0 80px rgba(191, 255, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .hero-copy {
    margin-top: 24px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 62ch;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .hero-copy strong {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .vision-strip {
    margin-top: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    max-width: 100%;
    padding: 18px 22px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid var(--line-default);
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .vision-strip::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--accent-primary), transparent);
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  .vision-strip p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  .focus-grid {
    margin-top: 32px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .focus-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    min-height: 280px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 26px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line-default);
    background: var(--bg-card);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: all 220ms ease;
  }

  .focus-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, currentColor, transparent);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 220ms ease;
  }

  .focus-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: var(--line-strong);
    background: var(--bg-card-hover);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .focus-card:hover::before {
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .focus-card.nano {
    color: var(--accent-primary);
  }

  .focus-card.insights {
    color: var(--accent-secondary);
  }

  .badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-self: flex-start;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: 0.3rem 0.65rem;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    border: 1px solid currentColor;
    background: transparent;
  }

  .nano .badge {
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    border-color: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.2);
    background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.08);
  }

  .insights .badge {
    color: var(--accent-secondary);
    border-color: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.2);
    background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.08);
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.65rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .focus-card p {
    margin-top: 14px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .jump {
    margin-top: auto;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding-top: 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    transition: gap 160ms ease;
  }

  .focus-card:hover .jump {
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .jump::after {
    content: 'â†’';
    transition: transform 160ms ease;
  }

  .focus-card:hover .jump::after {
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .focus-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .focus-card {
      min-height: 240px;
    }
  }
</style>
